Twelve Apostles
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:twelve holders of large valuable Maori land holdings in Hawke's Bay, subject of a special commission in 1873
Origin: [none]
Register: historical
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
